          Shop Smarter with <br class="hidden sm:inline" />
          <span
            class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-sky-400 via-indigo-300 to-purple-400"
          >
            SwiftBasket
          </span>
        </h1>

        <p
          class="text-base sm:text-lg lg:text-xl text-slate-300 max-w-xl leading-relaxed"
        >
          Discover premium products, unbeatable deals, and lightning-fast
          shopping experiences curated specifically for your lifestyle.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 pt-2">
          <a
            href="/store/products"
